ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: THIS CLASS IS THE BEST EVER. Seriously, you would be a fool not to take it. The extreme epicness of CHEM 562 continues, only with MORE AWESOME. You probably won't be able to build a gigantic telescope next year :( but you'll learn a huge amount of valuable skills, I'm sure. TAKE IT!

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This class is absolutely essential for everyone from physicists and chemists to geophysicists. Without this course, I would be a skill less Neanderthal. Multitudes of undergrads and grad students use the SCL stundent shop on a regular basis. Please continue to support it generously and allow Dave to share his plethora of expertise with us lucky individuals.
